          "input_ue_unconnectable": {}
        }
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "## Main Model\n\n[GGUFs](https://huggingface.co/unsloth/Z-Image-GGUF/tree/main)\n\nGoes in models/diffusion_models\n\nBF16 gguf recommended if you have at least 16 GB VRAM.\n\nQ8 will just barely fit in 8 GB VRAM if you know how to squeeze it.\n\nQ6_K will fit in 8 GB VRAM easily.\n\n## Text Encoder\n\nQwen 3 4b [Normal](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image/tree/main/split_files/text_encoders) | [gguf](https://huggingface.co/Qwen/Qwen3-4B-GGUF/tree/main)\n\nGoes in models/text_encoders\n\nGrab the biggest normal one if you have 10GB+ VRAM, otherwise grab the Q8 GGUF.\n\n## VAE\n\n[Flux 1 VAE](https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image/tree/main/split_files/vae)\n\nGoes in models/vae"
      ],
      "color": "#2a363b",
      "bgcolor": "#3f5159"
    },
